      "file_path": "components/pm-subscription-handler/pmsh_service/mod/api/services/subscription_service.py",
      "patchset_number": 2,
      "line": 430,
      "message": "The two scenarios captured here are either Filtering or Locking. And all the MG's would either be in Locking or Filtering state that gets captured in one go. And we will not miss anything.",
